snippet.title: Star Impact - Teaser
snippet.description:
Star Impact 
Coming to Steam in May 2019
PC, Mac OSX, and Linux

Hi Everyone, we are working diligently here at Me Games to wrap up Star Impact for release on Steam in May 2019. Hopefully we can build up an audience and community around the game.
If you have any questions, feel free to comment below.

https://www.megamesdev.com/

Music
Nightstop – Harrison Ford: https://youtu.be/Iij7U6eE5lo

🎮 STEAM ➔ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1052030/Star_Impact/

🐦 TWITTER ➔ https://twitter.com/realMeGames

📷 INSTAGRAM ➔ https://www.instagram.com/me.games.dev

🎭 FACEBOOK ➔ https://www.facebook.com/MeGamesDeveloper

━━━━━━━━━━━━━

💻 Development Blog ➔ https://www.megamesdev.com/dev-blog

💻 Mailing List ➔ https://www.megamesdev.com/#subscribe

━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Please like, follow, and subscribe.
